               <msContents>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; 1st, 3rd, 5th, 6th, 16th and 17th lines in the incipit page; titles of the paragraphs, chapters, discourses and prayers; the 1st and 3rd line of the prayer on fol. 2r; elements of the punctuation signs.</rubric>
