                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
                  <!--The data in the items below refers to other items. please remove this items and move the information to the appropriate place.-->
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <note>The text contains 34 "paragraphs" (አንቀጽ) with numbers indicated by numerals (e.g., ፳, ፴ወ፪) or written out (ቀዳማዊ, ራብዕ); but other wise discourses (ነገር) (fols. 46ra, 54rb, 56vb), chapters (ምዕራፍ) (fols. 69rb, 101rb, 107va), prayers (ጸሎት) (fols. 87va, 92rb, 111vb) and the concluding homily (fol. 145ra).</note>
                  </msItem>
