                           <locus target="#2r">Fol. 2r</locus>: Scribe's exhortation to the Lord.<q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 2r: ለዛቲ፡ ብርዕየ፡ ዘወጠንክዋ፡ አሥምራ፡ እግዚኦ፡ ወአሠንያ፡ ወአፈጽመኒ፡ በዳህና፡ ወበሰላ[ም] </q>
                           <q xml:lang="en">This pen of mine which I have begun [to use], accept it o Lord and beautify it and help me finish it [my work] in wellness and peace.</q>
                           The note is written in hand a. The first and the last lines are rubricated.
